siccom.sim

Class ParameterFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • siccom.sim.ParameterFile

  • public class ParameterFile
extends java.lang.Object
    This class takes a File or InputStreamReader object as a reference and opens and read the existing parameter file:
    • It reads all lines and creates a ParmEntry object for every to store the information.
    • It stores the read values by the name of the entry. If multiple entries with the same name exists a warning dialog is displayed.
    • The first line is, usually the header, is read and processed like every line.
    The read information can be retrieved by invoking getValue(String) and getComment(String)ï¿½where the read value or the comment are returned for the provided key. If the key does not exist null is usually returned.
    Author:
    hoehne
